Tablet-Based


Contact Sales








Secure. Reliable. Cost-effective.

A point-of-sale solution should be all of these and scalable to your needs. 
Your business is unique, so we offer customized, versatile and comprehensive systems designed to grow as your company does. With Heartland, your POS becomes the center of your commerce—allowing you to integrate with your other applications, such as payroll, and marketing and loyalty programs.
Most importantly, we offer our proprietary POS security technology to provide you with unparalleled protection.












Why It’s Best to be Out-of-Scope

                        Heartland’s “Out of Scope” solution takes the POS system completely out of the payment authorization process… keeping card data secure. Learn more about this solution by watching this video.
                    

 

                Learn More
            














Need Help Financing Your POS System?

                        Heartland can help you get the loan you need through our Heartland Lending service. We focus on what’s most important to you so that we can pair you with a loan that best matches your needs.
                    

 

                Learn More
            



















Software 


                    Innovative POS software is at the core of Heartland Commerce. Our priority is to provide software that makes running your business easier—and more efficient. With Heartland’s POS software, you can:

Bring your store online
Track inventory and reduce theft
Attract more customers and build loyalty with marketing and rewards programs
Streamline administrative tasks
Create and view customizable reports












































Hardware 


                    Secure, PCI-compliant hardware is vital to an effective POS system. Heartland partners with quality terminal manufacturers to provide you with options designed to fit your budget and POS hardware system needs.
                
















Tablet-Based 


                    Accepting mobile payments is convenient for your customers—and you. Turn a tablet or smartphone into a terminal with Heartland’s mobile POS system. Our tablet-based point-of-sale systems come with all the features of traditional POS software. Quickly and securely process customer transactions, accurately track sales and inventory, optimize employee labor and create detailed business reports—all from a mobile device. Mobile POS terminals offer several advantages:

Small footprint suited for businesses with limited workspace
Intuitive design that reduces training and support time
Easily integrates with traditional PC-based POS systems
Available with a variety of flexible purchase or rental options
Ideal for applications such as line busting, remote sales and more where mobility is a requirement.



























 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 







